{"tid":141054,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如果人死左係無意識","createTime":"2017-03-02T15:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-05T05:33:08.000Z","uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ae6480c0ab26a872d077c941d57da569485011a1","tid":141054,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T15:22:02.000Z","msg":"咁人生其實冇乜意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 在生時係好人定壞人，百年歸老定係比isis𨧡頭......都冇乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f420c9e7d72050b12596c068b79424b5a87e5953","tid":141054,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T15:26:06.000Z","msg":"人生得意須盡歡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a75776a319f18194fa7443d30df44b9b37e179","tid":141054,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T15:27:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人生得意須盡歡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcfb237b620e203bf3c496e627b8aba82ca47e32","tid":141054,"uid":39921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T15:28:15.000Z","msg":"你都假設左，重可以有咩結果"},{"pid":"621cdb62ebd41eaed8153d64d68a01a57e43d0fd","tid":141054,"uid":86488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T15:32:59.000Z","msg":"重點係你點樣過埋仲有意識嘅日子"},{"pid":"c431558c266e89ccaa8d11ccb7df5603f7a5bced","tid":141054,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T15:34:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>人生得意須盡歡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n喺呢個前設下做秦檜咪好過做岳飛"},{"pid":"29d99e0724ce2fdeb283558d8f46746591cabb6a","tid":141054,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T15:35:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>人生得意須盡歡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n喺呢個前設下做秦檜咪好過做岳飛</blockquote><br />\nyes<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0701dad584d27b2cc9aa18fbb0d5a3e544a6220b","tid":141054,"uid":83152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T15:36:01.000Z","msg":"唸唸下其實出世都幾無謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ff3a3f320db1b915eef107991405f0f5b4bf70a","tid":141054,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T15:38:37.000Z","msg":"生命體意識水平到咗某階段就會開始思考存在意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係好事"},{"pid":"4564599391ab5e0ec83f5b90a4b7b69572127cd0","tid":141054,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T06:30:36.000Z","msg":"有冇哲學撚講雨句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b296c2b381e71b160b67a58dda34143f2351675","tid":141054,"uid":86901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:49:18.000Z","msg":"從結果論去睇人死咗應該係冇任何嘢<br />\n<br />\n好隔硬講下 人死後可能仲有啲嘢架喎<br />\nhesiod theogony話有個死神(夜神同黑暗神個仔)係會帶啲死人去underworld<br />\n蘇格拉底死之前有講過人死係肉體同靈魂(soul)既分離<br />\n所以人在生時應該做既嘢係purify the soul同attain virtue....<br />\n跟住有條友就話咁樣好驚驚喎<br />\n蘇格拉底就答佢 靈魂係不死架 唔洗怕唔洗怕<br />\n到耶蘇出場 就話好人會跟我去天堂 壞人會去地獄<br />\n佛教講既極樂世界<br />\n仲有會變鬼 投胎 等等等等<br />\n<br />\n當然可以話 經驗同現實世界搵唔倒答案<br />\n<br />\n不過想拋多一句<br />\n相信命運/瞑瞑中自有主宰？<br />\n人以為命運係掌握係自己手中<br />\n一話其實一早已經跟咗一個既定劇本？<br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999"},{"pid":"d245a884c5fd0dac2311ea96161c90464f3cea65","tid":141054,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:51:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生命體意識水平到咗某階段就會開始思考存在意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係好事</blockquote><br />\n我中一比人罰完抄, 唔記得係關於生命嘅野, 幅個下已經會係咁諗生命意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deeb00022316ab0b1a655cfc49b2a1194b4f876b","tid":141054,"uid":39921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T08:58:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>從結果論去睇人死咗應該係冇任何嘢<br />\n<br />\n好隔硬講下 人死後可能仲有啲嘢架喎<br />\nhesiod theogony話有個死神(夜神同黑暗神個仔)係會帶啲死人去underworld<br />\n蘇格拉底死之前有講過人死係肉體同靈魂(soul)既分離<br />\n所以人在生時應該做既嘢係purify the soul同attain virtue....<br />\n跟住有條友就話咁樣好驚驚喎<br />\n蘇格拉底就答佢 靈魂係不死架 唔洗怕唔洗怕<br />\n到耶蘇出場 就話好人會跟我去天堂 壞人會去地獄<br />\n佛教講既極樂世界<br />\n仲有會變鬼 投胎 等等等等<br />\n<br />\n當然可以話 經驗同現實世界搵唔倒答案<br />\n<br />\n不過想拋多一句<br />\n相信命運/瞑瞑中自有主宰？<br />\n人以為命運係掌握係自己手中<br />\n一話其實一早已經跟咗一個既定劇本？<br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999</blockquote><br />\n要多吸收，睇吓自己既信仰偏向邊一邊"},{"pid":"79926a216bb4d01caf92a991a13f6db2330da8bd","tid":141054,"uid":20972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T23:46:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/05/074613_3346a174d1d513e750c81fc0aa0f269d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F05%2F074613_3346a174d1d513e750c81fc0aa0f269d.jpg&h=9927fdfb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"849a665fba0e192446edfd5cbbc4a5f1456e55b8","tid":141054,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-04T23:56:01.000Z","msg":"其實你怎知道這是你所認知的世界<br />\n有沒有聽過Brain in a vat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"586ee9eeeeaf819afd9f241091b24fb7cee3d4f7","tid":141054,"uid":37979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T00:06:08.000Z","msg":"如果記憶無繼承效果， 其實都唔算同一靈魂。"},{"pid":"6abb8fcbe82fe756846904d227334799e66be53f","tid":141054,"uid":70192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T00:09:06.000Z","msg":"有無電影講類似既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95eca20f810bc766f5138e60befaa75983afe8df","tid":141054,"uid":74497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T00:09:08.000Z","msg":"享受個過程"},{"pid":"7f0a2537ac3831246f4972ce4665faef85aab41c","tid":141054,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T01:12:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁人生其實冇乜意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 在生時係好人定壞人，百年歸老定係比isis𨧡頭......都冇乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n死左唔知有冇啦<br />\n但你仲有生命果時 唔計植物人果類<br />\n咁你係有意識 有感情<br />\n係仲有生命既時候 你做既野對自己係有意義<br />\n而且呢份意義你死後都存在<br />\n因為你過程中可以影響到年輕既人<br />\n有書有紀錄既更可以一直傳落去<br />\n你討論呢個人生意義著眼點應該係有生命既時候 而非死後<br />\n冇左生命都冇左你當下既人生"},{"pid":"fb3ec97920eeb15541ba9f030fc4367d81e653c7","tid":141054,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T01:14:55.000Z","msg":"我自己就三十<br />\n仲係低層職位 又冇興趣 又悶 又冇朋友<br />\n呢種生活我都覺冇意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b70e136b7a2ea3dcdba2e4255530e0c6458b5c","tid":141054,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T05:33:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}